```
Activation: Requires 5/7 NASAg regional approval

Phase 1 (Containment):
  - Freeze all license issuance
  - Isolate compromised systems
  - Activate emergency cryptographic keys

Phase 2 (Assessment):
  - International forensic investigation
  - Determination of scope and impact
  - Development of recovery plan

Phase 3 (Recovery):
  - Gradual restoration with enhanced security
  - Verification of all systems before reactivation
  - Implementation of lessons learned
```

